{"tid":957502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最可愛女國中生是她！　13歲「抖音女孩」網讚：天使臉蛋","createTime":"2018-12-27T05:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T09:46:44.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"944b66ca801357bb9227bf2baa5d4c61379a2493","tid":957502,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3791/d3791210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3791%2Fd3791210.jpg&h=8cc99d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本舉辦「JC Misscon 2018」選美活動，要選出全日本最可愛的國中生，26日在東京舉行決賽，最後由13歲出身北海道的富本愛琉奪下冠軍。同時她也是抖音小有名氣的網紅，相較於前一屆飽受酸評，最新一屆冠軍被狂讚「可以接棒當偶像了！」<br />\n <br />\n富本愛琉現在是國中二年級，且已經是小學生時尚誌《Nicopuchi》的讀者模特兒，更跨海開設抖音帳號，吸引不少粉絲關注。她擁有臥蠶大眼、纖細身材，當聽到自己的名字被念出來時嚇了一跳，戴上后冠、披風，展現絕佳自信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3791/d3791209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3791%2Fd3791209.jpg&h=84fd92ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據日媒《Modelpress》報導，選美比賽「「JCMisscon」已經舉辦第二屆，冠軍將被大型藝能公司簽下經紀約，第一屆由來自福岡的有川沙姫獲得，不過獲獎前三名皆被網友酸評「這在班上當第一美也有點困難」，相隔一年評價提升，同時第二屆冠軍是從3000人報名中脫穎而出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2980/d2980121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2980%2Fd2980121.jpg&h=36f534d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3791/d3791255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3791%2Fd3791255.jpg&h=99c5c2ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cac64e152e44f8c7721c38a17fdeac56cad272f","tid":957502,"uid":107364,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6db920b7bb4ee7db52da0b6bc71d7a363fbdb3b6","tid":957502,"uid":30150,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"玩抖音的都係臭雞黎"},{"pid":"7c0cf